                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
{% endfor %}

{% form 'contact' %}

{% if form.posted_successfully? %}
    <div class="modal fade modal-centre" id="modal-success" tabindex="-1" role="dialog"
         aria-labelledby="modal-success-label">
        <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><span
                                aria-hidden="true">&times;</span></button>
                    <h4 class="modal-title" id="modal-success-label">Message Received</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-12 col-xs-12 text-center">
                            <p>Thanks for getting in touch.</p>
                            <p>We'll respond to your enquiry shortly.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
{% endif %}

{% if form.errors %}
    <div class="modal fade modal-centre" id="modal-failure" tabindex="-1" role="dialog"
         aria-labelledby="modal-failure-label">
        <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><span
                                aria-hidden="true">&times;</span></button>
                    <h4 class="modal-title" id="modal-failure-label">Contact Form Errors</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-12 col-xs-12 text-center">
                            <p>Your contact form has errors. To submit your form, make the following changes and try
                                again:</p>
                            {% for field in form.errors %}
                                <p>The {{ field | capitalize | replace: 'Body', 'Message' }}
                                    field {{ form.errors.messages[field] }}.</p>
                            {% endfor %}
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
{% endif %}

<div class="modal fade modal-centre" id="modal-contact" tabindex="-1" role="dialog"
     aria-labelledby="modal-contact-label">
    <div id="contactFormWrapper" class="modal-dialog" role="document">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
                </button>
                <h4 class="modal-title" id="modal-contact-label">Contact Us</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-6 col-xs-12">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <select required id="contactFormSubject" class="form-control placeholder"
                                    name="contact[subject]">
                                <option value="" disabled selected hidden>what are you getting in touch about?</option>
                                <option value="Online Store">- online store</option>
                                <option value="Purchasing Eyewear">- purchasing eyewear</option>
                                <option value="Wholesale enquiry">- wholesale enquiry</option>
                                <option value="Bespoke Eyewear">- bespoke eyewear</option>
                                <option value="Press">- press</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-6 col-xs-12">
                        <input class="form-control" type="text" required id="contactFormName" placeholder="name"
                               name="contact[name]">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6 col-xs-12">
                        <input class="form-control" type="email" required id="contactFormEmail"
                               placeholder="email address" name="contact[email]">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-12">
                        <textarea required id="contactFormMessage" placeholder="leave your message here..."
                                  name="contact[body]"></textarea>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
                <p>
                    <input class="btn btn-primary" type="submit" id="contactFormSubmit" value="Submit"/>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="modal fade modal-centre" id="modal-sizing-guide" tabindex="-1" role="dialog"
     aria-labelledby="modal-sizing-guide-label">
    <div id="contactFormWrapper" class="modal-dialog" role="document">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><span
                            aria-hidden="true">&times;</span></button>
                <h4 class="modal-title" id="modal-sizing-guide-label">A Guide To Eyewear Sizing</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-xs-12">
                        <p>Sunglasses tend to be larger than eyeglasses, so your sunglasses size will most likely be
                            different than your eyeglasses size. With sunglasses, you have more freedom to choose within
                            a
                            wider range of sizes, since the fit does not need to be as precise.</p>

                        <p>There can be quite a few different kinds of numbers and markings inside your frame, and not
                            all
                            of them are relevant to the size.</p>

                        <p>The eye size and bridge size are often located next to one another, sometimes separated by a
                            square box icon. The temple size may immediately follow those two sets of numbers, or have
                            some
                            other info in between.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
{% endform %}